casebody.head_matter:
In the MATTER OF DISCIPLINE OF Neal Jonathan BLAHER
No. D-3057
Supreme Court of the United States.
January 13, 2020
Neal Jonathan Blaher, of Orlando, Florida, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court, and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
